### Bước 6 — Quy tắc Render Markdown → HTML

Khi convert nội dung Markdown sang HTML cho từng section, áp dụng:

**Checklist items:**
```
- [ ] Task APP-01: ...  →  <li class="task-todo"><span class="checklist-icon">⬜</span> Task APP-01: ...</li>
- [x] Task DB-01: ...  →  <li class="task-done"><span class="checklist-icon">✅</span> Task DB-01: ...</li>
```

**Progress counter** (từ dòng `> Progress: X / Y tasks`):
```html
<div class="progress-wrap">
  <div class="progress-header">
    <span>Tasks Progress</span>
    <span><strong>X</strong> / Y completed</span>
  </div>
  <div class="progress-bar">
    <div class="progress-fill" style="width: [X/Y*100]%"></div>
  </div>
</div>
```

**Mermaid blocks:**
```html
<div class="mermaid-wrap">
  <div class="mermaid" data-source="[mermaid code]">
[mermaid code]
  </div>
</div>
```

**Code blocks (non-mermaid):**
```html
<pre><code class="language-[lang]">[escaped code]</code></pre>
```

**Metadata lines** (`> Key: Value`):
```html
<blockquote>[Key]: [Value]</blockquote>
```

**Tables:** Convert trực tiếp sang `<table>` HTML chuẩn với class `.doc-content`.

**Sections** (`##` headings): Bọc mỗi `##` section vào `.doc-section` với collapsible behavior:
```html
<div class="doc-section" id="[slug]">
  <div class="section-header" onclick="toggleSection(this)">
    <h2>[Section Name]</h2>
    <span class="collapse-icon">▾</span>
  </div>
  <div class="section-content">
    [content]
  </div>
</div>
```

